# Privacy Policy

**Last updated:** June 2026

## No data collection

VolMaster collects no personal data. It does not track, profile, or transmit any information to any server, ever.

## Local storage only

Your volume settings are saved to your browser's local extension storage (`storage.local`). This data never leaves your device.

## Tab metadata

Tab titles, URLs, and favicons are read to display your tabs in the popup. This data is used only within the popup and is never stored or transmitted.

## No network requests

VolMaster makes zero network requests. There are no analytics, no crash reporters, no update servers, and no external dependencies of any kind.

## No third parties

The extension is entirely self-contained. No third-party code or services are used.
